channel.title: Login rs2hd
channel.description:
The problem happened recently while refactoring my source. It gives me this as usual:
[IMG]http://i45.tinypic.com/nqa6gh.png[/img]
but when I try to connect, it says "Performing login..." and after a while, it says: "Connection timed out. Please try using a different server.".
I replaced most of the login related files to be sure it wouldn't be this, but it still doesn't work. Any idea on how to fix?
